%%time
DECIMAL = 0  # for rounding
SYMBOL = "BTCJPY"

## Load Data
trade = pd.concat([
    load_data(["2025-05-01", "2025-05-22"], table="MarketTrade", venue="*", symbol="BTCJPY"),
    load_data(["2025-05-01", "2025-05-22"], table="MarketTrade", venue="*", symbol="XBTUSD"),
])
trade["term_amount"] = trade.amount * trade.price / 1e6
trade["latency"] = (trade["timestamp"] - trade.market_created_timestamp).dt.total_seconds() * 1e3

rate = pd.concat([
    load_data(["2025-05-01", "2025-05-22"], table="Rate", venue="*", symbol="USDJPY"),
    load_data(["2025-05-01", "2025-05-22"], table="Rate", venue="*", symbol="BTCJPY"),
    load_data(["2025-05-01", "2025-05-22"], table="Rate", venue="*", symbol="XBTUSD"),
])

## Preprocessing
# best price
best = rate.set_index("timestamp").groupby(["venue", "sym"])[["best_bid", "best_ask"]].resample("5s", label="right").last().unstack(level=[0, 1])
best = best.swaplevel(0, -1, axis=1).swaplevel(0, 1, axis=1).replace(0, np.nan).ffill()

# traded price
tprice = trade.set_index("market_created_timestamp").groupby(["venue", "sym"]).price.resample("5s", label="right").last().unstack(level=[0, 1])

# exec price
exec_price = trade.set_index("market_created_timestamp").shift(freq="-100ms").groupby(["venue", "sym", "side"]).price.resample("5s").agg(["min", "max"])
exec_price = exec_price.unstack(level=[0, 1, 2]).swaplevel(0, -1, axis=1)
sell = exec_price.loc[:, ix[-1, :, :, "min"]][-1]
sell.columns = ["sell_"+"_".join(c[:1]) for c in sell.columns]

buy = exec_price.loc[:, ix[1, :, :, "max"]][1]
buy.columns = ["buy_"+"_".join(c[:1]) for c in buy.columns]
exec_price = buy.join(sell)

# mid prices
mid = rate.set_index(["timestamp"]).groupby(["venue", "sym"]).mid_price.resample("5s", label="right").last().unstack(level=[0, 1]).ffill()
mid[("bitmex", "XBTJPY")] = mid.bitmex.XBTUSD * mid.gmo.USDJPY
mid = mid.drop([("gmo", "USDJPY"), ("bitmex", "XBTUSD")], axis=1)
mid.columns = mid.columns.get_level_values(0)
mid = mid.mask(mid.div(mid.rolling("10min").mean()).sub(1).abs().ge(0.03), np.nan).ffill()

Bitflyer¶

In [5]:
venue = "bitflyer"
maker_fee = 1  # [bps]
taker_fee = 1  # [bps]

results = []
for freq, offset in tqdm(itertools.product(["1min", "5min", "10min"], [1, 3, 5, 10])):
    
    # Create dataset
    global_mid = mid.drop("bitbank", axis=1).mean(axis=1).to_frame("mid")
    dev = mid.div(global_mid.values).sub(1).mul(1e4)
    dev_ma = dev.rolling(freq).mean()
    dev_smooth = dev - dev_ma
    ask = (dev_ma + offset).div(1e4).add(1).mul(global_mid.values)
    bid = (dev_ma - offset).div(1e4).add(1).mul(global_mid.values)
    data = pd.concat([
        ask[venue].rename("ask"),
        bid[venue].rename("bid"),
        mid[venue].rename("mid"),
        exec_price[[f"buy_{venue}", f"sell_{venue}"]].set_axis(["buy", "sell"], axis=1),
        best[venue][SYMBOL].set_axis(["best_bid", "best_ask"], axis=1),
        dev_ma[venue].to_frame("dev_ma"),
        dev_smooth[venue].to_frame("dev_smooth"),
        global_mid.mid.pct_change().rolling(freq).std().mul(np.sqrt(12 * 1440 * 365) * 100).to_frame("vol"),  # 5sec刻みなので x12 x1440 x365
        np.sign((global_mid.mid - global_mid.mid.rolling(freq).mean())).rename("ma_sign"),
    ], axis=1)
    data.index.name = "timestamp"
    
    # run foreach params
    for params in tqdm(ParameterGrid({
        "horizon": 12 * np.array([5, 10, 60]),
        "use_best_price_for_exit": [True, False],
        "exit_spread": [0, 1, 5],
        "sl_level": [30, 50, np.nan],
        "tp_level": [30, 50, np.nan],
        "vol_threshold": [30, 50, 70],
    })):
        res = run_dev_mm(data, decimal=DECIMAL, **params)
        res["fee"] = res.entry_otype.replace({"limit": maker_fee, "market": taker_fee}) + res.exit_otype.replace({"limit": maker_fee, "market": taker_fee})
        res["pl"] = res.pl_raw - res.fee
        res["venue"] = venue

        params["offset"] = offset
        params["freq"] = freq
        res["params"] = str(params)
        results.append(res)
        
results = pd.concat(results)
results.to_parquet(base_path.joinpath(f"{venue}_{SYMBOL}.parquet"))

desc = results.groupby("params").pl.describe()
desc["sharpe"] = desc["mean"] / desc["std"]
desc["total_pl"] = desc["mean"] * desc["count"]

# argmax total pl
res = desc.query("count > 100").sort_values("sharpe", ascending=False).drop_duplicates("mean").head()
display("Argmax Sharpe", res)
params = res.index[0]
sub = results.query("""params == @params""")
sub.set_index("entry_timestamp").pl.cumsum().div(100).plot(figsize=(8, 4))
plt.show()

In [11]:
venue = "bitbank"
maker_fee = -2  # [bps]
taker_fee = 12  # [bps]

results = []
for freq, offset in tqdm(itertools.product(["1min", "5min", "10min"], [1, 3, 5, 10])):
    
    # Create dataset
    global_mid = mid.drop("bitbank", axis=1).mean(axis=1).to_frame("mid")
    dev = mid.div(global_mid.values).sub(1).mul(1e4)
    dev_ma = dev.rolling(freq).mean()
    dev_smooth = dev - dev_ma
    ask = (dev_ma + offset).div(1e4).add(1).mul(global_mid.values)
    bid = (dev_ma - offset).div(1e4).add(1).mul(global_mid.values)
    data = pd.concat([
        ask[venue].rename("ask"),
        bid[venue].rename("bid"),
        mid[venue].rename("mid"),
        exec_price[[f"buy_{venue}", f"sell_{venue}"]].set_axis(["buy", "sell"], axis=1),
        best[venue][SYMBOL].set_axis(["best_bid", "best_ask"], axis=1),
        dev_ma[venue].to_frame("dev_ma"),
        dev_smooth[venue].to_frame("dev_smooth"),
        global_mid.mid.pct_change().rolling(freq).std().mul(np.sqrt(12 * 1440 * 365) * 100).to_frame("vol"),  # 5sec刻みなので x12 x1440 x365
        np.sign((global_mid.mid - global_mid.mid.rolling(freq).mean())).rename("ma_sign"),
    ], axis=1)
    data.index.name = "timestamp"
    
    # run foreach params
    for params in tqdm(ParameterGrid({
        "horizon": 12 * np.array([5, 10, 60]),
        "use_best_price_for_exit": [True, False],
        "exit_spread": [0, 1, 5],
        "sl_level": [30, 50, np.nan],
        "tp_level": [30, 50, np.nan],
        "vol_threshold": [30, 50, 70],
    })):
        res = run_dev_mm(data, decimal=DECIMAL, **params)
        res["fee"] = res.entry_otype.replace({"limit": maker_fee, "market": taker_fee}) + res.exit_otype.replace({"limit": maker_fee, "market": taker_fee})
        res["pl"] = res.pl_raw - res.fee
        res["venue"] = venue

        params["offset"] = offset
        params["freq"] = freq
        res["params"] = str(params)
        results.append(res)
        
results = pd.concat(results)
results.to_parquet(base_path.joinpath(f"{venue}_{SYMBOL}.parquet"))

%%time
DECIMAL = 0  # for rounding
SYMBOL = "ETHJPY"

## Load Data
trade = pd.concat([
    load_data(["2025-05-01", "2025-05-22"], table="MarketTrade", venue="*", symbol=SYMBOL),
    load_data(["2025-05-01", "2025-05-22"], table="MarketTrade", venue="*", symbol="ETHUSD"),
])
trade["term_amount"] = trade.amount * trade.price / 1e6
trade["latency"] = (trade["timestamp"] - trade.market_created_timestamp).dt.total_seconds() * 1e3

rate = pd.concat([
    load_data(["2025-05-01", "2025-05-22"], table="Rate", venue="*", symbol="USDJPY"),
    load_data(["2025-05-01", "2025-05-22"], table="Rate", venue="*", symbol=SYMBOL),
    load_data(["2025-05-01", "2025-05-22"], table="Rate", venue="*", symbol="ETHUSD"),
])

## Preprocessing
# best price
best = rate.set_index("timestamp").groupby(["venue", "sym"])[["best_bid", "best_ask"]].resample("5s", label="right").last().unstack(level=[0, 1])
best = best.swaplevel(0, -1, axis=1).swaplevel(0, 1, axis=1).replace(0, np.nan).ffill()

# traded price
tprice = trade.set_index("market_created_timestamp").groupby(["venue", "sym"]).price.resample("5s", label="right").last().unstack(level=[0, 1])

# exec price
exec_price = trade.set_index("market_created_timestamp").shift(freq="-100ms").groupby(["venue", "sym", "side"]).price.resample("5s").agg(["min", "max"])
exec_price = exec_price.unstack(level=[0, 1, 2]).swaplevel(0, -1, axis=1)
sell = exec_price.loc[:, ix[-1, :, :, "min"]][-1]
sell.columns = ["sell_"+"_".join(c[:1]) for c in sell.columns]

buy = exec_price.loc[:, ix[1, :, :, "max"]][1]
buy.columns = ["buy_"+"_".join(c[:1]) for c in buy.columns]
exec_price = buy.join(sell)

# mid prices
mid = rate.set_index(["timestamp"]).groupby(["venue", "sym"]).mid_price.resample("5s", label="right").last().unstack(level=[0, 1]).ffill()
mid[("bitmex", "ETHJPY")] = mid.bitmex.ETHUSD * mid.gmo.USDJPY
mid = mid.drop([("gmo", "USDJPY"), ("bitmex", "ETHUSD")], axis=1)
mid.columns = mid.columns.get_level_values(0)
mid = mid.mask(mid.div(mid.rolling("10min").mean()).sub(1).abs().ge(0.03), np.nan).ffill()

venue = "gmo"
maker_fee = 0  # [bps]
taker_fee = 0  # [bps]

results = []
for freq, offset in tqdm(itertools.product(["1min", "5min", "10min"], [1, 3, 5, 10])):
    
    # Create dataset
    global_mid = mid.drop("bitbank", axis=1).mean(axis=1).to_frame("mid")
    dev = mid.div(global_mid.values).sub(1).mul(1e4)
    dev_ma = dev.rolling(freq).mean()
    dev_smooth = dev - dev_ma
    ask = (dev_ma + offset).div(1e4).add(1).mul(global_mid.values)
    bid = (dev_ma - offset).div(1e4).add(1).mul(global_mid.values)
    data = pd.concat([
        ask[venue].rename("ask"),
        bid[venue].rename("bid"),
        mid[venue].rename("mid"),
        exec_price[[f"buy_{venue}", f"sell_{venue}"]].set_axis(["buy", "sell"], axis=1),
        best[venue][SYMBOL].set_axis(["best_bid", "best_ask"], axis=1),
        dev_ma[venue].to_frame("dev_ma"),
        dev_smooth[venue].to_frame("dev_smooth"),
        global_mid.mid.pct_change().rolling(freq).std().mul(np.sqrt(12 * 1440 * 365) * 100).to_frame("vol"),  # 5sec刻みなので x12 x1440 x365
        np.sign((global_mid.mid - global_mid.mid.rolling(freq).mean())).rename("ma_sign"),
    ], axis=1)
    data.index.name = "timestamp"
    
    # run foreach params
    for params in tqdm(ParameterGrid({
        "horizon": 12 * np.array([5, 10, 60]),
        "use_best_price_for_exit": [True, False],
        "exit_spread": [0, 1, 5],
        "sl_level": [30, 50, np.nan],
        "tp_level": [30, 50, np.nan],
        "vol_threshold": [30, 50, 70],
    })):
        res = run_dev_mm(data, decimal=DECIMAL, **params)
        res["fee"] = res.entry_otype.replace({"limit": maker_fee, "market": taker_fee}) + res.exit_otype.replace({"limit": maker_fee, "market": taker_fee})
        res["pl"] = res.pl_raw - res.fee
        res["venue"] = venue

        params["offset"] = offset
        params["freq"] = freq
        res["params"] = str(params)
        results.append(res)
        
results = pd.concat(results)
results.to_parquet(base_path.joinpath(f"{venue}_{SYMBOL}.parquet"))

%%time
DECIMAL = 3  # for rounding
SYMBOL = "XRPJPY"

## Load Data
trade = pd.concat([
    load_data(["2025-05-01", "2025-05-22"], table="MarketTrade", venue="*", symbol=SYMBOL),
    load_data(["2025-05-01", "2025-05-22"], table="MarketTrade", venue="*", symbol="XRPUSD"),
])
trade["term_amount"] = trade.amount * trade.price / 1e6
trade["latency"] = (trade["timestamp"] - trade.market_created_timestamp).dt.total_seconds() * 1e3

rate = pd.concat([
    load_data(["2025-05-01", "2025-05-22"], table="Rate", venue="*", symbol="USDJPY"),
    load_data(["2025-05-01", "2025-05-22"], table="Rate", venue="*", symbol=SYMBOL),
    load_data(["2025-05-01", "2025-05-22"], table="Rate", venue="*", symbol="XRPUSD"),
])

## Preprocessing
# best price
best = rate.set_index("timestamp").groupby(["venue", "sym"])[["best_bid", "best_ask"]].resample("5s", label="right").last().unstack(level=[0, 1])
best = best.swaplevel(0, -1, axis=1).swaplevel(0, 1, axis=1).replace(0, np.nan).ffill()

# traded price
tprice = trade.set_index("market_created_timestamp").groupby(["venue", "sym"]).price.resample("5s", label="right").last().unstack(level=[0, 1])

# exec price
exec_price = trade.set_index("market_created_timestamp").shift(freq="-100ms").groupby(["venue", "sym", "side"]).price.resample("5s").agg(["min", "max"])
exec_price = exec_price.unstack(level=[0, 1, 2]).swaplevel(0, -1, axis=1)
sell = exec_price.loc[:, ix[-1, :, :, "min"]][-1]
sell.columns = ["sell_"+"_".join(c[:1]) for c in sell.columns]

buy = exec_price.loc[:, ix[1, :, :, "max"]][1]
buy.columns = ["buy_"+"_".join(c[:1]) for c in buy.columns]
exec_price = buy.join(sell)

# mid prices
mid = rate.set_index(["timestamp"]).groupby(["venue", "sym"]).mid_price.resample("5s", label="right").last().unstack(level=[0, 1]).ffill()
mid[("bitmex", SYMBOL)] = mid.bitmex.XRPUSD * mid.gmo.USDJPY
mid = mid.drop([("gmo", "USDJPY"), ("bitmex", "XRPUSD")], axis=1)
mid.columns = mid.columns.get_level_values(0)
mid = mid.mask(mid.div(mid.rolling("10min").mean()).sub(1).abs().ge(0.03), np.nan).ffill()

venue = "coincheck"
maker_fee = 0  # [bps]
taker_fee = 0  # [bps]

results = []
for freq, offset in tqdm(itertools.product(["1min", "5min", "10min"], [1, 3, 5, 10])):
    
    # Create dataset
    global_mid = mid.drop("bitbank", axis=1).mean(axis=1).to_frame("mid")
    dev = mid.div(global_mid.values).sub(1).mul(1e4)
    dev_ma = dev.rolling(freq).mean()
    dev_smooth = dev - dev_ma
    ask = (dev_ma + offset).div(1e4).add(1).mul(global_mid.values)
    bid = (dev_ma - offset).div(1e4).add(1).mul(global_mid.values)
    data = pd.concat([
        ask[venue].rename("ask"),
        bid[venue].rename("bid"),
        mid[venue].rename("mid"),
        exec_price[[f"buy_{venue}", f"sell_{venue}"]].set_axis(["buy", "sell"], axis=1),
        best[venue][SYMBOL].set_axis(["best_bid", "best_ask"], axis=1),
        dev_ma[venue].to_frame("dev_ma"),
        dev_smooth[venue].to_frame("dev_smooth"),
        global_mid.mid.pct_change().rolling(freq).std().mul(np.sqrt(12 * 1440 * 365) * 100).to_frame("vol"),  # 5sec刻みなので x12 x1440 x365
        np.sign((global_mid.mid - global_mid.mid.rolling(freq).mean())).rename("ma_sign"),
    ], axis=1)
    data.index.name = "timestamp"
    
    # run foreach params
    for params in tqdm(ParameterGrid({
        "horizon": 12 * np.array([5, 10, 60]),
        "use_best_price_for_exit": [True, False],
        "exit_spread": [0, 1, 5],
        "sl_level": [30, 50, np.nan],
        "tp_level": [30, 50, np.nan],
        "vol_threshold": [30, 50, 70],
    })):
        res = run_dev_mm(data, decimal=DECIMAL, **params)
        res["fee"] = res.entry_otype.replace({"limit": maker_fee, "market": taker_fee}) + res.exit_otype.replace({"limit": maker_fee, "market": taker_fee})
        res["pl"] = res.pl_raw - res.fee
        res["venue"] = venue

        params["offset"] = offset
        params["freq"] = freq
        res["params"] = str(params)
        results.append(res)
        
results = pd.concat(results)
results.to_parquet(base_path.joinpath(f"{venue}_{SYMBOL}.parquet"))

desc = results.groupby("params").pl.describe()
desc["sharpe"] = desc["mean"] / desc["std"]
desc["total_pl"] = desc["mean"] * desc["count"]

# argmax total pl
res = desc.query("count > 100").sort_values("sharpe", ascending=False).drop_duplicates("mean").head()
display("Argmax Sharpe", res)
params = res.index[0]
sub = results.query("""params == @params""")
sub.set_index("entry_timestamp").pl.cumsum().div(100).plot(figsize=(8, 4))
plt.show()

display("Argmax TotalPNL", res)
